{"tid":394902,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人用過洗鼻器？","createTime":"2017-09-10T11:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T04:17:45.000Z","uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4fb056b5fd7f3c28e4a6b9147e670a4d426845","tid":394902,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"我長期都有一邊鼻塞。我諗緊去洗鼻會唔會好D。<br />\n呢個好似幾唔錯。有冇人用緊?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tH9LCgvUNG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtH9LCgvUNG8&d=pHA8xSnmiKajWaFOQZ69K0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=562662f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tH9LCgvUNG8</a>"},{"pid":"0570f79927d025ea8bbfcddc36cafb128b26802b","tid":394902,"uid":94935,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"上次洗到甩哂鼻毛"},{"pid":"a7dee07120c72690f0b2717d04a7a718ab18065d","tid":394902,"uid":15862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"洗鼻時是咪用到口抖氣而唔會飲左啲水"},{"pid":"ee7e797f83bebe935e9938da64dd4fdd393a7a77","tid":394902,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"好想買。但用一兩次放埋一邊好似幾無謂"},{"pid":"fc220f72e7e0b2228938910964f46de5e815e73b","tid":394902,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次洗到甩哂鼻毛</blockquote><br />\n點洗到甩晒"},{"pid":"c44d3f593902779ebeed30e85ce389436154ba9b","tid":394902,"uid":45442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"用過<br />\n可以將鼻竇啲勁濃勁黃既鼻涕都洗埋出嚟<br />\n但鼻塞係鼻隔充血<br />\n洗完唔會通返晒，只係舒服少少"},{"pid":"6239eec56007aec2afbe78f2344b87b93785588e","tid":394902,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"我都係一邊長塞喎真係通到"},{"pid":"e99ac1c231cedcef3bd35fca03b961f1ea4833da","tid":394902,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"隔離有片啲人真係洗到啲污糟嘢出嚟"},{"pid":"8e2c4056d9731639f5b6031d0b8aa4b9267b8e85","tid":394902,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"有冇地方洗。醫生一定講咩正常唔洗 洗鼻之類"},{"pid":"9227c6ca8ade25674fe3627bd0d1369b141bd679","tid":394902,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離有片啲人真係洗到啲污糟嘢出嚟</blockquote><br />\n有冇片？"},{"pid":"044f5908976635dc751073b361e909c4d2f175c1","tid":394902,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/002943_6c12e80e6fd242ad17b6652ecab4e0fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F002943_6c12e80e6fd242ad17b6652ecab4e0fa.jpg&h=71a2845c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使買電動㗎，就咁買呢類型大容量，有個出水位係咁上下塞到鼻孔位就得。<br />\n<br />\n懶嘅可以買生理鹽水沖劑，慳錢嘅直接自己溝就得。每晚臨瞓前每邊鼻各洗一兩次就得，水温盡量暖水偏凍會舒服啲。"},{"pid":"2e7e7113bb7a00ff925fac870bf645eedcaafc0b","tid":394902,"uid":5955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/002943_6c12e80e6fd242ad17b6652ecab4e0fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F002943_6c12e80e6fd242ad17b6652ecab4e0fa.jpg&h=71a2845c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使買電動㗎，就咁買呢類型大容量，有個出水位係咁上下塞到鼻孔位就得。<br />\n<br />\n懶嘅可以買生理鹽水沖劑，慳錢嘅直接自己溝就得。每晚臨瞓前每邊鼻各洗一兩次就得，水温盡量暖水偏凍會舒服啲。</blockquote><br />\n香港係邊度買到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08de4e3ef93a907b9a852ca6642c2a8751b331b0","tid":394902,"uid":137041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"呢排電視都係咁有廣告講呢類產品"},{"pid":"86de2ab784e4ffbbba0a5a44e0a7407993bc7869","tid":394902,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/002943_6c12e80e6fd242ad17b6652ecab4e0fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F002943_6c12e80e6fd242ad17b6652ecab4e0fa.jpg&h=71a2845c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使買電動㗎，就咁買呢類型大容量，有個出水位係咁上下塞到鼻孔位就得。<br />\n<br />\n懶嘅可以買生理鹽水沖劑，慳錢嘅直接自己溝就得。每晚臨瞓前每邊鼻各洗一兩次就得，水温盡量暖水偏凍會舒服啲。</blockquote><br />\n香港係邊度買到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己唔係用呢款，你去藥房或者醫院問「洗鼻樽/器」呢啲Keywords應該買到。<br />\n<br />\n我自己用嗰款好的骰，容量好細要係咁refill　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839535262a6cdee790b54c2bbf75d3878b2b34a7","tid":394902,"uid":15143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:06:14.000Z","msg":"用左好耐，本身鼻水倒流，個樽係淘寶淘，自己用幼鹽溝水洗"},{"pid":"9fcc8042a9e30ba61ce23226775052ccb06c10bb","tid":394902,"uid":116028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"鼻竇炎，洗好咗。<br />\n一開始醫生話多啲洗我都唔信會好，感覺好hea。<br />\n但因為太多分泌物，每次洗完又的確舒服啲好訓啲，所以keep住訓前洗。<br />\n點知洗咗一個月好咗八成，不過洗鼻壺香港好難搵，又勁貴，我都係淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家仲有少少，但已經好咗勁多，洗幾日你就會摸索到點洗，不過記得如果啲水搞到痛就要落多少少鹽"},{"pid":"2e1fa5536898f60508d5eac8be903c9570c0678d","tid":394902,"uid":34787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:25:31.000Z","msg":"淘寶得架啦，手動自己溝自己禁，每晚洗係會有好轉"},{"pid":"402a8fe8ad0b6c509ce7e7a27d86daecfb70a05c","tid":394902,"uid":116028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼻竇炎，洗好咗。<br />\n一開始醫生話多啲洗我都唔信會好，感覺好hea。<br />\n但因為太多分泌物，每次洗完又的確舒服啲好訓啲，所以keep住訓前洗。<br />\n點知洗咗一個月好咗八成，不過洗鼻壺香港好難搵，又勁貴，我都係淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家仲有少少，但已經好咗勁多，洗幾日你就會摸索到點洗，不過記得如果啲水搞到痛就要落多少少鹽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/013129_ed8dc8a1f988c4cdee373c8e3507ae74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F013129_ed8dc8a1f988c4cdee373c8e3507ae74.jpg&h=4ede5699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我用呢款"},{"pid":"fcb8768eab5eff6a0bc7ef76ff48e05c9e923423","tid":394902,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"TB 有冇邊隻介紹？"},{"pid":"10b3aa093059a5c463ea5a060b3aba78986cc2c3","tid":394902,"uid":3509,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg&h=6888c5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長期用呢個。"},{"pid":"53829bb50d7c944d34fe9a17f8b42870bcd7d567","tid":394902,"uid":19421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg&h=6888c5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長期用呢個。</blockquote><br />\n我都帶用呢個 但好似治標唔治本咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c78689b124110c0c4c585f1faaa78238daa521","tid":394902,"uid":3509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg&h=6888c5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長期用呢個。</blockquote><br />\n我都帶用呢個 但好似治標唔治本咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，但就馬上通返。"},{"pid":"0ab657ac111c9ac8f25cb4891ae153e1e9da8d8f","tid":394902,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n但唔知應該點根治"},{"pid":"41d44759823ce346cd35e74909c5f9547e38017b","tid":394902,"uid":17543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg&h=6888c5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長期用呢個。</blockquote><br />\n長期用,每次有fd去日本都叫佢帶一箱翻黎"},{"pid":"bc360952fd35483571d7ee6b6a69e013d2d58792","tid":394902,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F184506_6ba5f6e058b2e9dffce9e2bbb5629d23.jpg&h=6888c5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長期用呢個。</blockquote><br />\n長期用,每次有fd去日本都叫佢帶一箱翻黎</blockquote><br />\n得呢隻先救到我<br />\n神藥"}]}